summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5439 for the improvement of 44th Avenue Southwest, from West Austin Street to a point 50 feet, more or less, south of West Portland Street; by constructing sewers and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 68495, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
